  "body": "When pushing large batches of BLS change, our beacon-api endpoint floods the signer, and we get nasty 500 errors.\n\nWe should implement a limit to the number we're going to accept per request.\n\nCurrently the local operation queue for BLS is around 10_000, maybe limiting to 5_000 would be a good starting point, as it's the signer queue that was getting flooded, not the operation queue (validation before adding to the op queue).",
